cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with semantic segmentation and 3D mapping, which are primarily computer vision and robotics topics. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.RO are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel CRF model for optimization, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with large-scale environments, which could also be categorized under computer graphics (cs.GR).
